{
  "stem": "23438.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She's gone to the states after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had normal secondary school classes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Very strict teachers, and we're trying to make it-- teachers were trying to make it as normal as possible.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember the girl who survived was called Hania Kohn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was Wanda Rechthand who was a gorgeous girl, with a very strong character.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll come back to her later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was Hala Piwnic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember the other two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The other thing we were doing, there was operating in the ghetto, a society called the Society of Advancing Agriculture Amongst Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we occupied a vacant block of land outside the hospital or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we dug out the concrete.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were planting flowers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were also breeding chicks-- chickens in an incubator.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was really more fun than anything else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we-- it kept us busy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One day, one of the girls picked a rose out of the flowers that we'd planted, and took it home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Next day, somebody sent her a note-- a Polish rhyme, saying-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] don't pick roses, Annie, said mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Roses are prickly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You'll cut your fingers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And roses are prickly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Annie picked a rose.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She pricked her finger and cried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's really hard to translate into English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But that's what it meant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a little rhyme.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the girl who picked the rose answered with another rhyme, saying, let's not mourn roses when the forests are burning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we had some-- we spent some time in that [INAUDIBLE] so-called garden.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Other than that, life in the ghetto was something terrifying and extremely strange.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
